50|$|In 2014, Kars4Kids {{released}} an app for Android, Kars4Kids Safety, {{which aims to}} prevent accidental deaths of children by parents forgetting them in their cars while the temperature is hot. The app syncs with the car's Bluetooth technology, to set off an automatic alert <b>when</b> <b>the</b> <b>phone’s</b> Bluetooth disconnects from the car’s.|$|R
