50|$|Third-party {{programs}} have been created, including software that will automatically change the screen orientation <b>when</b> <b>the</b> <b>phone</b> is tilted, programs that simulate {{the sounds of a}} Star Wars lightsaber <b>when</b> <b>the</b> <b>phone</b> is waved through the air, allow you to mute the phone by turning it face-down, and many more.|$|E
